{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624990/extras/character_hero_previews2.gif?t=1722517475\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624990/extras/Untitled_design__7_.png?t=1722517475\" /><br><br>What if Don't Starve had a baby with that one &quot;vampire&quot; game?<br><br><strong>Start with nothing</strong>, and craft your way into becoming a bullet hell menace to society.<br>A perfect hybrid gameplay loop enabled by a simple day/night system: <br><br>\u2600\ufe0f A survival game during the day<br>\ud83c\udf19 A survivors game during the night<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624990/extras/Steam_Description_Headers.gif?t=1722517475\" /><br><strong>\u21b3 The night is coming</strong><br><br>\u231b The clock is ticking. You need to prepare for the night.<br><br>Chop, mine and harvest resources. Cook and eat food to prevent starvation.<br>Craft structures, gears and weapons before they come!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624990/extras/three_panels_harvesting_615x250.gif?t=1722517475\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624990/extras/Steam_Description_Header_-_What_To_Expect.png?t=1722517475\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Day/night cycle loop.<br></li><li>Endless hordes of enemies at night.<br></li><li>Bigger and scarier mobs every day that passes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624990/extras/crafting_and_cooking_gif.gif?t=1722517475\" /><br><strong>\u21b3 Crafting and Cooking</strong><br><br></li><li>Survive the night! Prepare yourself, collect gears and craft weapons.<br></li><li>Grow permanently stronger by cooking and digesting food.<br></